dct_title_s: Cape Colony, Natal, Orange River Colony and part of Transvaal
dct_description_sm: George Philip & Son Ltd. ; The London Geographical Institute.
Provinces distinguished by coloring, with districts.
Shows railways (including proposed), submarine cables, steamer routes, roads, passes, mission stations, waterways, cities, regional names.
Dated from railways (specifically the incomplete railway between Adelaide and Alice, East Cape).
